cc:Work.dc:title: Flying Score Remix
cc:Work.dc:description: Remix of flying_score by J_Alves. Made each element able to be coloured individually by colour or by gradient. Added a shadow and gold leaf effect using the gradient editor. Note: even-though Document properties background is set to transparent, when saving as a Cairo png, it creates a png with a white background. To correct this Export Bitmap, choose dpi, give file a png extension, and this will create a png with correct transparency.
